attachments.title: Killer Tracks - Online Production Music Library Resource
attachments.text: Killer Tracks is an online production music library resource for producers and editors of film, television, radio, advertising, video games, trailers and interactive media content. Our leading catalog of pre-cleared, high quality background music features instrumental tracks and songs with vocals in a variety of genres, including Cinematic Score, Pop, Rock, Latin, Hip-Hop, Dance, Classical and more. We make music licensing fast and easy!

attachments.title: Let's Try Beats by stickwithjosh
attachments.text:
Trying to get better at making hip hop beats. I've never taken it very seriously and want to level up.

Trying to let myself publish things I'm not 100% proud of here, getting lots of stuff up and creating more songs / ideas is better than waiting for inspiration to strike or the perfect moment to happen. Some of these I'm very proud of and some are very embarrassing.
